# C:\Projects — one folder per project

- **MacTech** = one project folder: `C:\Projects\MacTech\`
  - `website\` — site code (open this in Cursor)
  - `design-assets\` — logos / art
- Never put MacTech files loose at `C:\Projects` root.
- **New brand:** `C:\Projects\_tools\new-project.ps1 -Name "Brand" -Inside "website"`
